color":"white"},{"tag":"postman","tech":"Postman","name":"DiTerminal","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"newman","tech":"Newman","name":"FaTools","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"express","tech":"Express","name":"FaJsSquare","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"webserver","tech":"webserver","name":"FaServer","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"nginx","tech":"NGINX","name":"FaServer","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"apitesting","tech":"APITesting","name":"FaServer","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"serveo","tech":"Serveo","name":"FaTools","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"ngrok","tech":"ngrok","name":"FaTools","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"localtunnel","tech":"Localtunnel","name":"FaTools","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"network","tech":"Network","name":"FaEthernet","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"lodash","tech":"Lodash","name":"FaJsSquare","size":20,"color":"white"},{"tag":"moment","tech":"Moment","name":"FaJsSquare","size":20,"color":"white"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>I've mentioned before that I hate testing mobile apps. One of the things I hate the\nmost is testing push notifications.</p>\n<p>But it turns out that Android does have one feature that makes this less hateful, if you\nknow where to look. Here's where to look:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Long press on home screen</li>\n<li>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Widgets</code> option</li>\n<li>Long press <code class=\"language-text\">Settings</code> and place a Setting shortcut on home screen</li>\n<li>Select <code class=\"language-text\">Notifications Log</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Now you've got a Notifications Log shortcut icon on your home screen showing you\nall the good stuff about your notifications that you previously had to pore through\nADB logs to find, like the complete message and the intent.</p>\n<img src='/android-notifications.png' width='300'>","frontmatter":{"title":"Android notifications","date":"March 02, 2020","tags":["android","mobile"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/android-notifications/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["392256161","551055924","63159454"]}